Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}因為是必需品…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我之前就給他手機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}但是他自己都沒有在用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}好像也沒有人打來給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}那孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}該不會沒有朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.00,0:04:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}真嗣的性格也許不適於交朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}妳知道「豪豬的距離」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(050,050)}豪豬？那種渾身是刺的
